title: 2 Bedroom 2 Bath 500 Brickell Split Plan Unit
posting_body: ['Beautiful 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom corner unit in the heart of Brickell.', 'Enjoy incredible city views from the 22nd floor of desirable 500 Brickell West Condo.', 'Live within walking distance to everything: restaurants, shops, Brickell City Centre, Downtown Miami and more.', '500 Brickell West offers top amenities, such as a pool with sundeck on the 11th floor, fitness center, sauna and steam rooms, theater room, sports room and much more', '*** Unfurnished ***', 'Asking Price : $4,100', 'You can either Text or Call :', 'Emmanuel CLODIC', 'show contact info', 'English/French/Spanish', 'London Foster Realty', 'NO BROKER/REALTOR CALLS', '1060,1050, ICON, JADE, THE SAIL, VUE, THE CLUB, THE MARK, BRICKELL KEY, ONE MIAMI, ONE BROADWAY, BRICKELL FIRST, LATITUDE, NEO VERTIKA, AXIS, 500, BRICKELL ON THE RIVER, MINT.', 'IVY.', 'WIND.', 'CENTRE.', '101.', 'BOND.', 'SLS.', 'THE EMERALD, SKYLINE, INFINITY, THE PLAZA, SOLARIS, THE LOFT DOWNTOWN, 4 MIDTOWN, MIDRISE, MIDTOWN 2, EPIC, VIZCAYNE, RIVERFRONT.', 'EVERGLADES ON THE BAY, 50 BISCAYNE, MARINA BLUE, 900 BISCAYNE, 888, TEN MUSEUM, BISCAYNE BLVD, MIDTOWN, DOWNTOWN, BRICKELL, MIAMI, 33130, 33131, 33132, 33129.']
